---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Chat API | Semyon Fox"
  description="POST /api/chat — ask Semyon, get a reply. Rate limited, agent-friendly."
>
  <section class="pt-20 pb-16 md:pt-28 max-w-3xl">
    <p class="text-dim text-xs uppercase tracking-[3px] mb-4">/docs</p>
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-3">
      Chat API
    </h1>
    <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed mb-10">
      A tiny endpoint that roleplays as me and answers questions about my
      projects, blog, and background. Rate limited, non-streaming, no auth.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xs text-dim uppercase tracking-[3px] mb-3">Endpoint</h2>
    <pre
      class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-xs text-heading mb-6 overflow-x-auto"><code>POST https://semyon.ie/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json</code></pre>

    <h2 class="text-xs text-dim uppercase tracking-[3px] mb-3">Request</h2>
    <pre
      class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-xs text-heading mb-3 overflow-x-auto"><code>{`{
  "messages": [
    { "role": "user", "content": "what are you working on lately?" }
  ]
}`}</code></pre>
    <ul
      class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed space-y-1 mb-8 list-disc pl-5"
    >
      <li>
        <code class="text-heading">messages</code>: 1-40 entries of <code
          class="text-heading">{`{ role, content }`}</code
        >.
      </li>
      <li>
        <code class="text-heading">role</code>: <code class="text-heading"
          >user</code
        > or <code class="text-heading">assistant</code>. Client-supplied <code
          class="text-heading">system</code
        > messages are dropped.
      </li>
      <li>
        <code class="text-heading">content</code>: non-empty string, max 4000
        chars.
      </li>
      <li>
        Server prepends a fixed system prompt and keeps the last 5
        user/assistant turns.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xs text-dim uppercase tracking-[3px] mb-3">
      Response (200)
    </h2>
    <pre
      class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-xs text-heading mb-3 overflow-x-auto"><code>{`{ "reply": "lately been grinding on the homelab..." }`}</code></pre>
    <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed mb-8">
      Single plain-text reply, ~300 token cap, non-streaming. No reasoning
      tokens are emitted.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xs text-dim uppercase tracking-[3px] mb-3">Errors</h2>
    <ul
      class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed space-y-1 mb-8 list-disc pl-5"
    >
      <li>
        <code class="text-heading">400</code> — invalid body (the reply contains the
        validation hint).
      </li>
      <li>
        <code class="text-heading">429</code> — rate limit hit (20 requests/minute/IP).
      </li>
      <li><code class="text-heading">502</code> — upstream model failure.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xs text-dim uppercase tracking-[3px] mb-3">Health</h2>
    <pre
      class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-xs text-heading mb-8 overflow-x-auto"><code>GET https://semyon.ie/api/chat/health → {`{ "status": "ok" }`}</code></pre>

    <h2 class="text-xs text-dim uppercase tracking-[3px] mb-3">
      Machine-readable
    </h2>
    <ul
      class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed space-y-1 mb-8 list-disc pl-5"
    >
      <li>
        OpenAPI 3.1: <a
          class="text-fox hover:underline"
          href="/api/chat/openapi.json">/api/chat/openapi.json</a
        >
      </li>
      <li>
        API catalog (RFC 9727): <a
          class="text-fox hover:underline"
          href="/.well-known/api-catalog">/.well-known/api-catalog</a
        >
      </li>
      <li>
        Markdown version of this page: <a
          class="text-fox hover:underline"
          href="/docs/chat-api.md">/docs/chat-api.md</a
        > (or send <code class="text-heading">Accept: text/markdown</code>)
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xs text-dim uppercase tracking-[3px] mb-3">Example</h2>
    <pre
      class="bg-surface border border-border rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-xs text-heading mb-12 overflow-x-auto"><code>curl -sS https://semyon.ie/api/chat \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d {`'{"messages":[{"role":"user","content":"hello!"}]}'`}</code></pre>

    <a href="/" class="text-fox text-sm hover:underline">&larr; back home</a>
  </section>
</Layout>
